sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Nasabah
    participant APP as Mobile App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant LOAN as Origination
    participant SCORE as Decision Engine
    participant SLIK as SLIK OJK
    participant DISB as Disbursement
    participant PGW as Payment Gateway
    participant NOT as Notification
    participant MQ as Event Bus

    U->>APP: Submit pengajuan + TTD akad
    APP->>GW: POST /loans/applications
    GW->>LOAN: forward
    LOAN->>LOAN: cek pinjaman aktif (BR-05)
    alt Ada pinjaman aktif
        LOAN-->>APP: 409 Conflict
    else Tidak ada
        LOAN->>LOAN: validasi limit & tenor (BR-04)
        LOAN->>MQ: publish LoanSubmitted
        LOAN-->>APP: 202 Accepted (DIPROSES)
        MQ->>SCORE: konsumsi
        SCORE->>SLIK: cek riwayat kredit
        SLIK-->>SCORE: skor & status
        SCORE->>SCORE: hitung grade + DBR (BR-06)
        alt APPROVE
            SCORE->>DISB: buat loan + jadwal
            DISB->>PGW: cairkan dana
            PGW-->>DISB: sukses
            DISB->>MQ: LoanApproved
        else REFER
            SCORE->>MQ: NeedManualReview (maker-checker)
        else REJECT
            SCORE->>MQ: LoanRejected
        end
        MQ->>NOT: konsumsi hasil
        NOT-->>U: Email & SMS (US-06)
    end
